== [[noun]] ==
:'''train''' (plural: trains)
#a line of connected [[car]]s pushed or pulled by one or more [[locomotive]]s, especially a [[railroad]] train which travels on a set of tracks.
#a group of animals, vehicles, or people that follow on another in a line; a [[caravan]] or [[procession]].
#a series of events or ideas which are interconnected; a train of events or a train of thought.
#a set of interconnected mechanical parts like the drive train of a car.
#that which is drawn along, like the part of a [[gown]] which trails behind the wearer.

